------------------------------------------------------------------------
TWEAK SLIDECASTING
------------------------------------------------------------------------

1. INSTALLATION

You have to create an bookmark with following url content:

javascript:(function(){var%20script=document.createElement('script');script.src='https://github.com/th3hamm0r/Tweak-Slidecasting/raw/master/tweak.js';document.getElementsByTagName('head')[0].appendChild(script);})()

This code will load and start the javascript file from the git repository.
As a result a red box with commands should appear at the top left corner.


2. BROWSER SUPPORT

Tested with:

 * Mozilla Firefox 3.6.11
 * Google Chrome 5.0.375.126
